' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
'  CROSS-PACKAGE RELATIONS
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
MahasiswaEntity ..> UniversitasResponse   : references university
StudentResponse ..> UniversitasResponse   : includes universitas
DataMahasiswaService ..> DataAbsensiService    : scoped by periode
PenilaianService ..> DataMahasiswaService  : scoped to mahasiswa
SertifikatService ..> DataMahasiswaService : scoped to mahasiswa
SuratKeteranganService ..> DataMahasiswaService : scoped to mahasiswa

note as ERD_NOTE
  <b>Entity Relationships (ERD — Database Level)</b>
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
  USER              1 ──── 1     MAHASISWA
  USER              1 ──── 1     MENTOR
  UNIVERSITY        1 ──── 0..*  MAHASISWA
  MENTOR            1 ──── 0..*  MENTOR_MAHASISWA
  MAHASISWA         1 ──── 1     MENTOR_MAHASISWA
  MAHASISWA         1 ──── 0..*  PERIODE_MAGANG
  PERIODE_MAGANG    1 ──── 0..*  ABSENSI
  PERIODE_MAGANG    1 ──── 0..*  DATA_KEGIATAN
  DATA_KEGIATAN     1 ──── 0..*  FILE_KEGIATAN
  PERIODE_MAGANG    1 ──── 0..1  PENILAIAN
  MENTOR            1 ──── 0..*  PENILAIAN
  PERIODE_MAGANG    1 ──── 0..1  SURAT_KETERANGAN_MAGANG
  PERIODE_MAGANG    1 ──── 0..1  SERTIFIKAT
end note

